data.name: sqlCommand1.CommandText
data.value: SELECT Obra.Idobra, Obra.Ubicacion, Obra.RFC, Razonsocial.Facturar, Zona.Zona, CASE Zona.Ubicación WHEN 1 THEN 'Local' WHEN 2 THEN 'Foranea' END AS Local FROM Obra LEFT OUTER JOIN Zona ON Obra.IdZona = Zona.IdZona LEFT OUTER JOIN Razonsocial ON Obra.IdCliente = Razonsocial.IdCliente AND Obra.RFC = Razonsocial.RFC WHERE (Obra.Origen = 1) ORDER BY Obra.Idobra
